data.title: [Solved] As of September 2021, Emmanuel Macron is the President of wh
data.meta_description:
The correct answer is France.Key Points


	France has picked Emmanuel Macron for five more years as the country's President.
	This
data.text:
-> SSC GD Constable 2025 Notification will be released on 27 August, 2024. For 2025 Cycle, the Computer Based Examination will be conducted on January-February 2025.

-> Earlier, Result was declared for the Constable (GD), 2024 Examination which was conducted from 20.02.2024 to 07.03.2024 and 30.03.2024 in the Computer Based Mode. The Successful Candidates have been provisionally shortlisted to appear in the PST / PET.

-> Also, Revised Vacancy was released. A total of 46,617 vacancies have been announced for the SSC GD Constable Exam 2024, out of which 41,467 vacancies are for Male Constables while 5,150 vacancies are for Female Constables.

-> Total 16185 candidates appeared for the exam.
